collectionMetadata.name: Stamp Duty Assessed, Annual
collectionMetadata.description: Number of instruments stamped and amount of stamp duty assessed by instrument types (sale and purchase agreement, lease agreement, mortgage agreement, share transfer and others) for Financial Year (FY)2006 to FY2022.

datasetMetadata.name: Stamp Duty Assessed by Type of Instrument
datasetMetadata.description: * There will be differences between the Stamp Duty Assessed (SDA) and the Tax Collection for Stamp Duty published on data.gov.sg. SDA is calculated based on the first stamp duty assessment and any additional stamp duty assessed, while Tax Collection is the total net amount of stamp duties collected, taking into account any tax refunds, adjustments and remissions.
